---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    I have been involved in Ruby application development since 2017 as a hobby, and it has been my primary activity since 2019. While my focus is primarily on backend development, I also have knowledge in frontend technologies and I'm open to working on frontend tasks as well. I have a passion for exploring new technologies and programming languages. I enjoy creating applications that have a real-world impact and help people. I have a good discipline and i like to work remotely and asynchronously. I have a professional level of English and have worked with clients from various countries, including Europe, the US, and others.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Master's degree in Applied Mathematics"
      subtitle="2017 - 2019 at Saint-Petersburg State University, Saint-Petersburg, Russia"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Bachelor's degree in Applied Mathematics"
      subtitle="2013 - 2017 at Saint-Petersburg State University, Saint-Petersburg, Russia"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Ruby Developer"
      subtitle="Oct 2022 - Present at xometry.de, remote"
    >
      Ruby on Rails backend developer
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Ruby Developer"
      subtitle="Sep 2020 - Aug 2021 at rubyroidlabs.com, remote"
    >
      Outsourcing various companies and clients, worked on multiple project including online stores, news feed hub, insurance start-up, e.t.c.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Ruby Developer"
      subtitle="Apr 2020 - Sep 2020 at igooods.ru, Saint-Petersburg, Russia"
    >
      Worked as backend developer in Retail team. Participated in integration of Auchan retail network, created dozens of various xml, xls, email reports. All kinds of various parsers, bulk uploads, big data import, e.t.c.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Ruby Developer"
      subtitle="Jul 2019 - Apr 2020 at sputnik8.com, Saint-Petersburg, Russia"
    >
      Ruby on Rails backend developer
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Web Development Intern"
      subtitle="Nov 2018 - May 2019 at Yandex, Saint-Petersburg, Russia"
    >
      Worked on internal service intented for frontend developers. Python, ReactJS, GraphQL
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="C++/CUDA Developer intern"
      subtitle="Jul 2018 - Aug 2018 at Joint Institute of Nuclear Research, Dubna, Russia"
    >
      Participated in summer student program. My project is "GNA framework: Implementation of GPU-based transformations"
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Quantitative research consultant"
      subtitle="Apr 2017 - Jul 2017 at WoldQuant LLC, Saint-Petersburg, Russia"
    >
      Building quantitative models aimed at predicting price movements of various asset classes.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
    <li>
      <a href="https://www.efset.org/cert/49rskH" target="_blank">EFSET English Certificate 87/100 (C2 Proficient)</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://www.coursera.org/account/accomplishments/certificate/ULVRXQQJXF7A" target="_blank">Basics of HTML & CSS</a>
      <p class="font-light text-sm">2022 at efset.org</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://www.coursera.org/account/accomplishments/certificate/95VX6JTVDL9B" target="_blank">Rails with Active Record and Action Pack</a>
      <p class="font-light text-sm">2018 at coursera.org</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://www.coursera.org/account/accomplishments/certificate/TBX6ZKNAYZUF" target="_blank">HTML, CSS, and Javascript for Web Developers</a>
      <p class="font-light text-sm">2018 at coursera.org</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://www.coursera.org/account/accomplishments/certificate/63M8RYYBC95H" target="_blank">Ruby on Rails: An Introduction</a>
      <p class="font-light text-sm">2017 at coursera.org</p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Skills</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-5 columns-2 mx-6">
    <li>HTML</li>
    <li>CSS</li>
    <li>Javascript</li>
    <li>SQL</li>
    <li>C++</li>
    <li>Python</li>
    <li>Ruby</li>
    <li>Ruby on Rails</li>
